# Videos Directory

Store all video files here.

## Usage:
- Place MP4 or WebM video files in this folder
- Reference them using absolute paths: `/videos/your-video.mp4`
- Example: `/videos/product-showcase.mp4`

## Supported Formats:
- MP4 (recommended)
- WebM

## File Naming:
- Use lowercase letters
- No spaces (use hyphens instead)
- Example: product-showcase.mp4, behind-the-scenes.mp4

## External Video Embeds:
For YouTube, TikTok, or Instagram Reels, use iframe embeds instead of this folder.
